  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0da5\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0db4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc5\u0d9a\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A crime is prevented by the wisdom of the Kaduwela police chief",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kaduwela police state that they were able to arrest three people in the luxury jeep who fled after being shot by the station commander of the Kaduwela police with sharp weapons and the thieves with drugs.",
        "A curved knife, three swords and five grams of stolen drugs were taken into custody by the police.",
        "Inspector Kan Weerasinghe, Station Commander of Kaduwela Police, was returning to the police station by radio car after finishing his duties at the annual deity statue exhibition at the Kaduwela Rankadu Pattini Temple, when he saw several people hurrying down from a luxury jeep parked in front of a petrol station in Kaduwela town, carrying sharp weapons. .",
        "Seeing the police radio car, the group turned back and ran to the jeep they had come in. As soon as they got into it, the station commander got out of the car, pointed a pistol at the jeep and ordered it to stop. Despite the police order, they shot at the wheels of the jeep when they were preparing to flee, but in the midst of the gunfire, the group went about 800 meters away from the jeep and stopped the vehicle on a side road, and three suspects were arrested.",
        "The station commander said that a special police team has been deployed to find the suspect who fled at that time",
        "The arrested suspects are residents of Ranala and Kaduwela and are between the ages of 26 and 38.",
        "The Kaduwela police say that two of the suspects involved in drug trafficking are people who have recently been released on bail from prison."
      ],
